import React from 'react'
import { Button, Item, Icon, Image, Label, Divider } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import "semantic-ui-css"
const EnterpCard = (props) => {
    console.log(props)
    return (
            <Item style={{width:"18vw",marginTop:"3vh"}} >
          
                <Item.Image size='tiny' src={props.img} />
                <Item.Content  verticalAlign="middle">
                    <Item.Header>{props.content}</Item.Header>
                    <Button onClick={props.onClick} style={{marginTop:"1vh"}} id={props.id}>Watch And Update
            <Icon name='right chevron' />
                </Button>
                </Item.Content>
            </Item>
    )
}

export default EnterpCard
